# The hosts a JVM build resolves its artifacts from, plus the endpoint `claude` itself talks to.
# Every other host is refused by the sandbox proxy with `403 Filtered`, so add the ones YOUR build
# needs (a company mirror, a plugin portal, a JDK download) rather than deleting these.
#
# One host per line, matched by fnmatch against the CONNECT hostname. tinyproxy ends an entry at
# the first whitespace or unescaped `#`, so a line starting with `#` is a comment and a hostname
# has to be bare.
#
# An edit here lands the next time the proxy starts: start-proxy.sh rebuilds the proxy image when
# the running container is enforcing anything else, and the loop starts the proxy on every run.
api.anthropic.com
repo1.maven.org
repo.maven.apache.org
repo.scala-sbt.org
repo.typesafe.com
oss.sonatype.org
